## Dimension: Completeness

**Definition**: The degree to which the synthesis addresses all aspects of the question using all available expert input without omission.

**Why This Matters**: Scientific advice must be comprehensive. Omitting question aspects or expert perspectives undermines the legitimacy and utility of the Delphi artefact for policymakers.

